long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
The extension helps you quickly move from search results in overpass-turbo to maps, street views, and aerials.

We support https://overpass-turbo.eu/ and https://maps.mail.ru/osm/tools/overpass/

More useful tools can be found on our telegram channel: https://t.me/northern_palmyra
